    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-maintained over the years. It's perfect for zipping around town or hitting the open road! I'd love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
