    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This chassis has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and recent rod bearing service to ensure long-term structural and internal integrity. The drivetrain features a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery and tactile feedback. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and upgraded dampers, maintaining the sharp turn-in and neutral handling characteristics synonymous with the M-division. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system overhaul and valve clearances\u2014are documented and within spec.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
