    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained specimen that exemplifies mechanical integrity and dependable performance. This vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who prioritizes long-term reliability and a refined driving experience. Its history of consistent upkeep ensures that it remains a robust and sophisticated choice within its class. We invite you to experience the seamless fusion of functionality and professional standards.",
