      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The chassis remains composed with the M-Variable differential lock and essential subframe reinforcement already completed to address floor-pan fatigue. Suspension kinematics are sharp, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is robust, with recent valve adjustments and rod bearing service documented. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning purist.",
